# Backend Railway/Docker build context allowlist.
# The backend image only needs Go module files, backend source, embedded
# migrations, and release metadata. Keep frontend/Vercel artifacts and local
# tooling caches out of Railway backend builds.
*

!Dockerfile
!railway.toml
!go.mod
!go.sum

!prometheus
!prometheus/**

!cmd
!cmd/**
!internal
!internal/**

# Test files are not needed to compile the production backend image.
**/*_test.go
internal/integration
internal/integration/**

# Guard against negated allowlist patterns re-including frontend package
# directories named "internal" from client/node_modules.
client
client/**

!.changes
!.changes/v*.md
.changes/unreleased
